Content: 

<p>When you encounter this error:</p><p class="ql-align-center"></p><p class="ql-align-center"><img src="data:image/png;base64,"></p><p>you just have to delete a .lock file and run the application again.</p><p>One of the file&#39;s position can be at*:</p><p></p><pre data-language="plain">
./home/{your-username}/.var/app/com.jetbrains.IntelliJ-IDEA-Community/config/JetBrains/IdeaIC2024.1/.lock
</pre><p></p><p>*Obviously - depending on your OS and where you initially installed the application it might not be the right directory.</p>
